LETTUCE: FRESH LETTUCE. BACON: BACON (CURED WITH WATER, SALT, SUGAR, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE. MAY ALSO CONTAIN DEXTROSE, FLAVORING, HONEY, POTASSIUM CHLORIDE, POTASSIUM LACTATE, SMOKE FLAVORING, SODIUM DIACETATE, SODIUM PHOSPHATE). PARMESAN CHEESE: (PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, SALT, LESS THAN 2% OF ENZYMES CHEESE CULTURE, CELLULOSE POWDER (TO PREVENT CAKING), POTASSIUM SORBATE (TO PROTECT FLAVOR), AGED 6 MONTHS. CREAM CHEESE: PASTEURIZED CREAM AND SKIM MILK, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SODIUM CASEINATE (MILK), SALT, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLE, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, LOCUST BEAN GUM, GUAR GUM, MALIC ACID, POTASSIUM SORBATE, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS.
